commands.name: az pipelines queue list
commands.syntax:
az pipelines queue list [--action {manage, none, use}]
                        [--detect {false, true}]
                        [--org]
                        [--project]
                        [--queue-name]

commands.name: az pipelines queue show
commands.syntax:
az pipelines queue show --id
                        [--action {manage, none, use}]
                        [--detect {false, true}]
                        [--org]
                        [--project]
